    <briefdescription>
<para>Structure provided in the <ref refid="group__mcumgr__callback__api__img__mgmt_1gga3fa2c42bade08cca1122e32f6315f107a19d53f0c0f6649858e97fbcecfbaf24c" kindref="member">MGMT_EVT_OP_IMG_MGMT_DFU_CHUNK</ref> notification callback: This callback function is used to notify the application about a pending firmware upload packet from a client and authorise or deny it. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Upload will be allowed so long as all notification handlers return <ref refid="group__mcumgr__mgmt__api_1ggac5d8757a7ca945c77f405764b85ad5c5a4201fc6fbffd1ca9ae99a2e90a40896f" kindref="member">MGMT_ERR_EOK</ref>, if one returns an error then the upload will be denied. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
